ZH: 若你不想去，那我们可以取消这个计划。
EN: If you don't want to go, then we can cancel this plan.

ZH: 若你需要帮助，随时告诉我。
EN: If you need help, let me know at any time.

ZH: 若你迟到了，可能错过了机会。
EN: If you are late, you may miss the opportunity.

ZH: 若他不同意，我们就没有其他选择。
EN: If he doesn't agree, we have no other choice.

ZH: 若我选错了路，你们应该告诉我。
EN: If I choose the wrong way, you should tell me.

ZH: 若天气好的话，我们可以去户外运动。
EN: If the weather is good, we can do outdoor activities.

ZH: 若你不努力，就无法取得成功。
EN: If you don't work hard, you will not succeed.

ZH: 若我们全力以赴，定会取得好成绩。
EN: If we do our best, we will achieve good results.

ZH: 若你不明白，请再问我一次。
EN: If you don't understand, please ask me again.

ZH: 若他到场，我们可以开始会议。
EN: If he arrives, we can start the meeting.

ZH: 若你遇到问题，可以给我打电话。
EN: If you encounter problems, you can call me.

ZH: 若你愿意，我可以帮你一起完成这项任务。
EN: If you are willing, I can help you complete this task.

ZH: 若你在学习上遇到困难，不要放弃。
EN: If you encounter difficulties in learning, don’t give up.

ZH: 若你加入我们的团队，我们一定会支持你。
EN: If you join our team, we will definitely support you.

ZH: 若需要休息，请告诉我。
EN: If you need to rest, please tell me.

ZH: 若你给我时间，我会改正错误的。
EN: If you give me time, I will correct my mistakes.

ZH: 若你能掌握好技能，你会很成功。
EN: If you can master the skills well, you will be very successful.

ZH: 若你听懂了老师的讲解，记得复习。
EN: If you understand the teacher's explanation, remember to review.

ZH: 若今天不下雨，我们就去郊外野餐。
EN: If it doesn't rain today, we will go for a picnic in the countryside.

ZH: 若你喜欢这个项目，我们可以一起合作。
EN: If you like this project. we can work together.
